profile_positions.description:
An award-winning digital marketing course for tomorrow's connected leaders, designed by Google, and certified by the IPA. Squares understand the whole digital picture - technology, strategy and execution.

6 month programme includes:
- Consumer and Brand behavior, focus on the role of social media;
- Disruptive thinking: innovation and business planning in a digital sphere;
- Digital marketing strategies across the Customer Journey;
- Think optimized: use analytics and data to improve your business performance;
- The ongoing revolution: operating in an ever-changing digital world.
